{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/articles/2019-03/CSS-scrolling-animation","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"GyeongSu Han's Github Pages","author":"@micalgenus","siteUrl":"https://micalgenus.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ffc4ae28-b5e1-5db7-b24e-0b49a4acf526","html":"<p>javascript에서 jQuery를 사용하지 않고, <code class=\"language-text\">window.scroll</code>을 사용해 스크롤위치를 변경시킬 때 애니메이션을 추가하고 싶었다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">scroll-behavior: smooth;</code>의 경우는 <a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-scroll-behavior\">다음</a>과 같이 지원하지 않는 브라우저가 많았다.</p>\n<p>이를 해결할 <a href=\"https://github.com/iamdustan/smoothscroll\">smoothscroll-polyfill</a>모듈이 있어 이를 사용하기로 했다.</p>\n<p>사용법은 다음과 같다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> smoothscroll <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'smoothscroll-polyfill'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// kick off the polyfill!</span>\nsmoothscroll<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">polyfill</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>사용하기 전에 선언을 해준다.</p>\n<p>그 후, 사용할 <code class=\"language-text\">window.scroll</code>을 다음과 같이 수정해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scroll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> top<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> left<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> behavior<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'smooth'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"categories":["Web"],"title":"CSS scrolling animation","date":"Mar 06, 2019","tags":["CSS"]}}},"pageContext":{"comments":true,"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/articles/2019-03/브라우저-CSS-기능-호완성-테스트","title":"브라우저 CSS 기능 호완성 테스트","comments":true}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/articles/2019-03/Create-React-App-Jest-error-over-nodejs-11.11","title":"Create React App Jest error over nodejs 11.11","comments":true}}}}}